\m \bd Tok Orait\bd*  
\m Dispela Buk Baibel i kam wantaim tok orait na lo bilong Creative Commons Attribution-Noncommercial-No Derivative Works license. Em i tok olsem \bd yu ken givim kopi long narepela manmeri.\bd* Yu ken wokim kopi na givim long husat i laikim. Tasol, yu mas tok klia dispela samting i kam long \it http://tokplesbaibel.org.\it* Yu no ken kisim mani na salim dispela. \bd Yu mas givim nating.\bd* Na tu, \bd yu no ken senisim Tok.\bd*  
\m Ol piksa i kam wantim ol Baibel na narapela buk i stap long dispela sait i gat tok orait long usim wantaim dispela samting tasol. Sapos yu laik narapela tok orait, yu mas askim husat i papa bilong copyright long dispela ol piksa.  
\m Sapos yu laik stretim samting i no orait long dispela tok orait, stretim tok, salim Buk Baibel, o tainim Tok bilong God long nupela tok ples, yu ken \bd askim mipela.\bd*  
\m Olgeta tok orait na lo long tok ples English i stap long \it http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/3.0/legalcode.\it*  
\m Sapos yu gat askim long dispela, \bd plis askim mipela.\bd* 
\pb   
\mt2 Ka Pepa suna igle paingwa  
\b  
\pb  
\mt2 Kuman Baibel ipre kamo mambuno dipene endungwa  
\p Neno Kande God kamo wakai Kuman yomba kanno mina beglkwa pre “Kuman Baibel” we dingwa. Kuman ka i ka pond kaima Simbu dumo suna i dingwa. Ana kamo yomba dimara i nunguno embriye kuri yambraglke ta upere pere ongwa. Kamo suwomta siyei yeglmere dinamga: “baptais” ya “bilip”. Kuman kanno mina ka ipre suwokagle dingwa: Baptais pre kamo i ta “kamambuno nigl pamga” te ta “kamambuno nigl bunga”. Bilip pre kamo i ta “pirngi dumga” te ta “pir mendumga”.  
\p Kanno i suwo akiye ya te ka tau ombugl dingwa i Kuman yomba yene pirkan erikwa. Ba Kuman ka Baibel beglmara kurita wirigl pangwa. Ipre pepa yaundo suwomta gumamugl pangwa i ene kere ana aglke kere erimbi, ana undinan pirpogl sindre pepa mundu kere piraglkwa.  
\p Ana komiti wagle ermogl Kuman ka sunawom dingwa pangwa igle mina God kamo wakai iyakete beglkwa. Kuman ka nem yomba meglkwa yene gunyei ana kanno mina wakai ere kere pirtre Neno Kande kamo pirpogl sinaglkwa.  
\p Ana Kuman kamo i Simbu dumo mina ka pond kaima pangwa. Te Papua Niugini mina yomba tau kanno pamara igle Kuman ka ende namba 3 ongwa. Ba pepa suwarata Kuman ka mina okna ta beglkwa yeikrukwa. Tamanga. Kuman ka i yene yomba ka dingwa kanno i-keunde pangwa. Ana yagl kruwo misinari okna tau ere beglkwa ba ka wu kuno pikrukwa. Ipre Neno God kamo Kuman ka mina ende muno beglkwa i wiriglgogl pango ana buglayungu tau mere dundungwa.  
\p P.N.G. Bible Society ya te SIL ermogl Kuman Baibel i boraglmendi akeple dimbrika. Simbu yomba gunyei yene kanno mina God kamo wakai kor aimande moraglkwa mambuno i kaima kan kere pir inaglkwa.  
\p Neno Kande God kamo kor aimande moraglkwa ka ikra erme Kuman ka mina bogl ipene endingwa. Kuman ka i Neno Kande God tongwa pre Simbu mina aimande giglendi pangwa pre Kuman Baibel beglkwa. Te ombugl Kuman kanno i okuwo wu taya pirkre te goglkrambedi Kuman ka beglkwa. Simbu yomba wakai pirtre Kuman Baibel i kere moraglkwa.  